project.name: Paper Reviewing Domain
project.description:
This model represents the challenge of assigning reviewer to paper in conferences, workshops and any academic event. In this model we have reserachers and their research areas, paper and their subjects (area). The goal is to do the best assignment based on a quality metric.This metric is based on the assigment of experts to paper.
Author: Tiago Stegun Vaquero

operator.name: assignReviewer
operator.constraints:
pre: r.isReviewer = true and r.papersAssigned < papersPerReviewer and p.reviewersAssigned < reviewersPerPaper and not(r.reviewerOf->includes(p)) and not(r.authorOf->includes(p))
post: r.papersAssigned = r.papersAssigned + 1 and p.reviewersAssigned = p.reviewersAssigned + 1 and r.reviewerOf = r.reviewerOf->including(p)

operator.name: assignRightReviewer
operator.constraints:
pre: r.isReviewer = true and r.papersAssigned < papersPerReviewer and p.reviewersAssigned < reviewersPerPaper and not(r.reviewerOf->includes(p)) and not(r.authorOf->includes(p)) and r.researchArea(a) = true and p.keywords(a) = true
post: r.papersAssigned = r.papersAssigned + 1 and p.reviewersAssigned = p.reviewersAssigned + 1 and r.reviewerOf = r.reviewerOf->including(p) and quality = quality + 5

operator.name: assignSpecialistReviewer
operator.constraints:
pre: r.isReviewer = true and r.papersAssigned < papersPerReviewer and p.reviewersAssigned < reviewersPerPaper and not(r.reviewerOf->includes(p)) and not(r.authorOf->includes(p)) and a1 <> a2 and r.researchArea(a1) = true and p.keywords(a1) = true and r.researchArea(a2) = true and p.keywords(a2) = true
post: r.papersAssigned = r.papersAssigned + 1 and p.reviewersAssigned = p.reviewersAssigned + 1 and r.reviewerOf = r.reviewerOf->including(p) and quality = quality + 10

classDiagram.name: Class Diagram
classDiagram.description:
This model represents the the challenge behind the process of assigning reviewers to papers in a conference, worhshop, or any academic event. Given the researchers, their profile (research area), and the paper together with the paper's subject area, the goal is to make the best,optimal assigment based on a quality metric. The quality metric is related to assigning papers to the relative experts (a good matching of the researchers' areas and the papers' subjects.
This model already considered authors that are in the review commitee.
